    "Figure 1 presents the decomposition results of STL with the default parameter values, using data from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention of the United States.",
    "(1) Y t = T t + S t + R t 2-Dimensional temporal convolution dense network (2DTCDN)TCN is an effective approach proposed for modeling long sequence.",
